# ============================================================
#  VS Code REST Client — test your backend without a browser
#  Install extension: "REST Client" by Huachao Mao
#  Then click "Send Request" above each line
# ============================================================

### 1. Health check — make sure server is running
GET http://localhost:5000/health

###

### 2. Dashboard stats — total hosts, online, offline, alerts
GET http://localhost:5000/api/stats

###

### 3. All hosts with CPU, RAM, ping
GET http://localhost:5000/api/hosts

###

### 4. Active alerts sorted newest first
GET http://localhost:5000/api/alerts

###
